STATE
v.
Dwain BELL 129P16-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2016

Dwain Bell, For Bell, Dwain.

Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, For State of N.C.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 19th of May 2016 by Petitioner for Objection to Order of Bill of Complaint Dismissed:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 18th of August 2016."
